Here's a bit of gossip I heard
at the baths.

rows.label: tlk45500153_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently Senator Roderich
was excavating some terrible
thing in Temperantia!

rows.label: tlk45500153_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I swear, those war hawks in the Senate
are always up to no good...

rows.label: tlk45500153_04_msg0004
rows.name:
But what I'd like to know is - who
actually benefited the most from
this whole debacle?
